  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Safety of Lubiprostone in Pediatric Subjects Aged ≥ 6 Years to &lt; 18 Years With Functional Constipation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, 6-month, Open-label Safety Study of Lubiprostone in Pediatric Subjects Aged ≥ 6 Years to &lt; 18 Years With Functional Constipation</official_title>
